title: Garbine Muguruza beats Safarova in WTA Finals debut

Wong Maye-E Garbine Muguruza beats Safarova in WTA Finals debut 
Garbine Muguruza of Spain makes a forehand return against Lucie Safarova of the Czech Republic during their singles match at the WTA tennis finals in Singapore on Monday, Oct. 26, 2015. (AP Photo/Wong Maye-E) Wong Maye-E Garbine Muguruza beats Safarova in WTA Finals debut 
Garbine Muguruza of Spain makes a backhand return against Lucie Safarova of the Czech Republic during their singles match at the WTA tennis finals in Singapore on Monday, Oct. 26, 2015. (AP Photo/Wong Maye-E) Wong Maye-E Garbine Muguruza beats Safarova in WTA Finals debut 
Lucie Safarova of the Czech Republic makes a forehand return against Garbine Muguruza of Spain during their singles match at the WTA tennis finals in Singapore on Monday, Oct. 26, 2015. (AP Photo/Wong Maye-E) Wong Maye-E Garbine Muguruza beats Safarova in WTA Finals debut 
Garbine Muguruza of Spain makes a backhand return against Lucie Safarova of the Czech Republic during their singles match at the WTA tennis finals in Singapore on Monday, Oct. 26, 2015. (AP Photo/Wong Maye-E) Posted: Monday, October 26, 2015 7:09 am | Updated: 8:00 am, Mon Oct 26, 2015. Garbine Muguruza beats Safarova in WTA Finals debut Associated Press | 
SINGAPORE (AP) â€” Second-seeded Garbine Muguruza had a successful debut at the WTA Finals, beating Lucie Safarova 6-3, 7-6 (4) Monday.
